         <abstract>
            <p>A method is proposed for simulating the effects of dimensional variation from geometric dimensioning and tolerancing (GD&amp;T) specifications. The method converts GD&amp;T specifications into equivalent covariance matrices which are needed in the statistical simulation of random processes. Examples are given to show how the method can be implemented.</p>
